# G-middleware — wrap a route with a chi middleware

Run `gofasta g middleware <METHOD> <path> <middleware-ref>
--dry-run --json` (e.g. `gofasta g middleware POST
/orders/{id}/archive auth.RequireRole("admin")`).

If the generator reports `ROUTE_ALREADY_WRAPPED`, the middleware is
already applied — confirm with the user before re-running.
Otherwise apply the planned patch.
